            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The school's infrastructure is really nice.All the staff arr very well behaved and the teachers are very friendly with the students .The school provides a wide range of extra curricular activities along with studies,which is very helpful for a child's mental and physical development.\nThe building are very clean and airy which improves a child's hygiene. The stud3nts are also very friendly and of adaptive nature The unity between all the students,is a special thing we can see in this school.The transport is amazing with more than 15 buses. I definitely advice u to choose this school for a child's development in all fields.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
