          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the best School. Discipline, Co-curricular activities, swimming, sports plays a wide role in a child's life along with study; all of which are encouraged in the school along with studies. My son secured AIR 5 in ICSE 2022 from this school. All teaching and non teaching staffs are very cordial. The school is having highly qualified faculties who guides each and every child one to one basis. Workshops on each subject before the final exams is add-on.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
